recommend_tutors.bio: My name is Jovee and I am from the Philippines. I am a graduate of Bachelor of Science in Secondary Education Major in English. I have been teaching English online and offline for more than three years now. I've handled Chinese and Filipino kids and adults too. I enjoy teaching kids that are beginners because I find it a blessing, especially when they have finally executed the word or the sound that you've been teaching them. In my previous years of teaching, I've learned and gathered some strategies and techniques  that can help me teach students of various levels. Guaranteed that I will be of great assistance in honing your communication skills. My goal is to touch the hearts of my students to love learning endlessly. Let us work together and make learning more fun!
recommend_tutors.education: Bachelor of Science in Secondary Education- Major in English
recommend_tutors.experience: ESL teacher and Call Center Representative
recommend_tutors.interests: I love gardening and reading story books to the kids.

recommend_tutors.bio: I am Mary Jane Francia; they call me Teacher Jane for short. I am from the Philippines. I've been teaching English for quite some time now. I can teach learners of different ages. I am a caring, loving, and understanding teacher. I am here to help you how to improve your speaking, listening, and writing skills in English. My style of teaching is fun and interactive class one-on-one. Teaching is my passion, and I am ready to meet and teach learners around the world, and you're welcome in my class. Let's make Learning English fun and exciting. See you!
recommend_tutors.education: Bachelor of Secondary Education Major in Biological Science  and Certified T.E.F.L. Teacher
recommend_tutors.experience: I have been teaching English for one year as an ESL tutor. I've handled Chinese, Japanese, and Korean learners. I can teach learners of different ages. I tried teaching learners aged 6-23 years old, and the oldest is 66 years old.
recommend_tutors.profession: I have been a practice teacher in a school and a home-based and office online ESL tutor  2020-2022.
recommend_tutors.interests: I like composing songs and poems, sightseeing,  going on adventures,  taking care of dogs, cooking, traveling, and most especially, l love teaching and teaching learners.
